column2: select a.artistid, a.name as artist, count (g.genreidid) as numClassical from chinook.artist a inner join chinook.album b on b.artistid = a.artistid left outer join chinook.track t on t.albumid = b.albumid left outer join chinook.Genre g on g.genreid = t.genreid and g.name = # group by a.artistid, a.name order by a.name
